messages.message:
Hello!  Are there any US based folks who could help me take a look at an issue with Arch today?

Arch has a POV environment in their own Azure (so i cant give you direct access, but can screenshare...).  I am able to copy a folder _from_ an account workspace into an organizational workspace, but once the folder has landed, I am unable to copy it within that organizational workspace.

cc. @JD
It seems like it is able to copy just 1 of the ~100 files or so
